%% WSS relay packet flow: NSC /client <-> NSGW <-> NSN /relay
%% Source: tests/docker/nsgw-mock/src/wss-relay.ts + src/index.ts + crates/tunnel-ws/
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant NSC as NSC (tunnel-ws client)
    participant GWC as NSGW /client<br/>clientSessions
    participant GWM as NSGW stitch tables<br/>connectorStreamToClient
    participant GWR as NSGW /relay<br/>activeSessions
    participant NSN as NSN (tunnel-ws client)
    participant SVC as Target service

    Note over NSC,NSN: Bootstrap: NSN already connected to /relay -> activeSessions has entry

    NSC->>GWC: WSS upgrade /client<br/>sessionId=client-1
    Note over GWC: clientSessions[client-1] created

    NSC->>GWC: Open frame s_id=42<br/>target 1.2.3.4:80/tcp
    GWC->>GWM: allocate connectorStreamId=0x10000001<br/>pick first activeSessions entry (relay-1)
    GWM->>GWR: Open frame s_id=0x10000001<br/>target 1.2.3.4:80/tcp
    GWR->>NSN: binary WsFrame (Open)
    NSN->>SVC: TCP connect
    SVC-->>NSN: ok

    loop payload loop
        NSC->>GWC: Data s_id=42, bytes
        GWC->>GWM: lookup connectorStreams[42]<br/>=> {0x10000001, relay-1}
        GWM->>GWR: Data s_id=0x10000001
        GWR->>NSN: binary WsFrame (Data)
        NSN->>SVC: write
        SVC-->>NSN: read
        NSN-->>GWR: Data s_id=0x10000001
        GWR-->>GWM: lookup connectorStreamToClient[0x10000001]<br/>=> {client-1, 42}
        GWM-->>GWC: Data s_id=42
        GWC-->>NSC: binary WsFrame (Data)
    end

    NSC->>GWC: Close s_id=42
    GWC->>GWR: Close s_id=0x10000001 (via stitch)
    GWR->>NSN: Close
    NSN-->>GWR: CloseAck s_id=0x10000001
    GWR-->>GWC: CloseAck s_id=42 (via stitch)
    GWC-->>NSC: CloseAck

    Note over NSC,NSN: Fallback: no NSN on /relay -> NSGW opens direct TCP via net.createConnection
